 class DefineFontInfo
           This tag maps a glyph font (defined with DefineFont) to a device font, providing a font name, style attributes (e.g. bold, italic) and a table of characters matching the glyph shape table contained in the corresponding DefineFont tag, thereby defining a one-to-one mapping between glyphs and characters.
 class DefineFontInfo2
           Like DefineFontInfo, this tag also maps a glyph font (defined with DefineFont) to a device font, providing a font name, style attributes (e.g. bold, italic) and a table of characters matching the glyph shape table contained in the corresponding DefineFont tag, thereby defining a one-to-one mapping between glyphs and characters.
